==Arabic==
===Etymology===
From {{ARchar|[[قراءة]]}} (qirā’a, "reading", "recitation"), from {{ARchar|[[قرأ]]}} (qará’a, "to declaim", "to recite").

===Proper noun===
'''{{ARchar|القرآن}}''' (al-qur’ān)

# the [[Qur'an|Qur’an]] (The [[Islamic]] holy book).

